name: Bounty Hunter – Miss Jane
description:
Explore an open Wild West frontier full of cowboys, bandits and more unnatural enemies in Bounty Hunter- Miss Jane, the third person shooter adventurous game.

Run & gun your way through dessert landscape as you embark on a mission to collect bounties against the forces of evil.

In this kill-or-be-killed land, you’ll rewarded heavy bounty for each boss kill. Take on 30 missions with a great variety of challenges for you to overcome. Take to the Arena in the most action packed shooting game. Center your attack to defeat powerful bosses.

Bounty Hunter – Miss Jane is a favorite for all ages, from those who grew up with classic arcade action games. The fun never dies!

Features:

✔Take on Challenging boss bounties
✔Plenty of power ups
✔Awesome graphics & soundtrack
✔Optimized for Android Phones and Tablets!

Download now & experience the adventurous, action packed, third person shooter game.
